    {
      "instruction": "<p>Line a separate baking tray with <strong>baking paper</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>ultimate vegan burger patties</strong> to the lined tray and put the tray in the oven for 10-12 min or until cooked through</p><p>Combine your <strong>mayo </strong>and <strong>tomato ketchup</strong> in a bowl – this is your <strong>ketchup mayo</strong></p>",
