    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>mature cheddar style block</strong> into 1 slice[s] per person</p><p>Once the patties have cooked through, remove the tray from the oven and top each patty with a <strong>mature cheddar style slice</strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>brioche buns</strong> in half and add them to the other side of the tray</p><p>Return the tray to the oven for 3-4 min or until the mature cheddar style slice has melted and the brioche is warmed through</p>",
